This is an Example Support Statement for the AL2022 Tech Preview. In this example, the end of life of Amazon Linux 2022 would be June 2027.From this point, the Amazon Linux 2022 packages (listed below) will no longer, receive any updates from AWS. This support period is an EXAMPLE ONLY, and may differ at GA date.
